Freshly-made canapes. Dressed to perfection and ready to be a hit at Jel's mother's party.

Garlic-seared trout with potatoes, created so ancient humans could share Einar's love of fishing. Hook fish more quickly for a short time.

Hanging your pots and pans on the wall not only saves space, it makes you look like a professional chef.

Harder, raw, lumber cut right from a tree.

Hassian made a sandwich for you. For some reason. Looks tasty, though!
